Title: Thaldraszus
Description:
Alexstrasza the Life-Binder is arranging a meeting of the Seat of the Aspects to discuss the threat of the Primalists.

She has put out a call for any willing adventurers to come help.
ObjectivesText: Travel to Valdrakken and meet with Alexstrasza the Life-Binder.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Travel to Valdrakken and meet with Alexstrasza the Life-Binder.
